### Node Installation steps on Mac:
- Installation with Brew:
    - brew update
    - brew install node

- Upgrade Node
    - brew update
    - brew upgrade node

- Error on installation of npm on mac
    - Error: module.js:487
    throw err;
    ^

    Error: Cannot find module 'semver'
    
    - Solution
        - brew update
        - brew uninstall node
        - brew install node
        - sudo chmod -R 777 /usr/local/lib
        - brew install 
        - brew postinstall node
        
 This has worked for me !
